	categories to priorities. Rename -weighing- functions to
	-weighted-. Rewrite some of the implementations.
	(planner-rank-calculate-urgency-from-deadline): More flexible
	implementation.
	(planner-rank-test-algorithm): Rewrite to not use loop defvar.

